mical processing may\naffect their observed C/O over the few Gyrs between formation and observation.\nOur population reproduces the general mass-metallicity trend of the solar\nsystem and qualitatively reproduces the C/O-metallicity anti-correlation that\nhas been inferred for the population of characterized exoplanetary atmospheres.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 29 Oct 2019 10:26:20 GMT"}],"update_date":"2019-12-04"}
