and treated\ninto mainly two parts, most or all types of attacks towards WSNs and IoT are\ninvestigated under that umbrella: \"Passive Attacks\" and \"Active Attacks\".\nUnderstanding these attacks and their associated defense mechanisms will help\nto pave a secure path towards the proliferation and public acceptance of IoT\ntechnology.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 29 Oct 2019 15:09:54 GMT"}],"update_date":"2019-11-19"}
